{"type":"step-attempt","step":"cross-boundary-invariants","sessionId":"13a89af3-31bd-4222-8604-5d48268674c5","outcome":{"verdict":"approved","findingsPath":"specrunner/changes/pipeline-selection-capability-gate/cross-boundary-invariants-result-002.md","error":null,"toolResult":{"ok":true,"approved":true,"findings":[],"observations":[{"severity":"low","file":"src/core/command/pipeline-run.ts","title":"pipeline: design-only + custom reviewers → zombie steps in composed descriptor (functional impact: zero)","rationale":"When pipeline: design-only is selected and specrunner/reviewers/*.md files exist, jobState.reviewers is snapshotted non-empty. composeReviewerDescriptor(DESIGN_ONLY_DESCRIPTOR, reviewers) appends zombie steps (custom reviewers + regression-gate) and their transitions to the composed descriptor. Since DESIGN_ONLY_DESCRIPTOR.transitions has design→success→end, the zombie steps are never reached and code-fixer (referenced in zombie transitions but absent from the steps map) is never invoked. No existing code reads state.reviewers and assumes reviewer steps were executed. Functional correctness is unaffected; the orphaned reviewers field is a data consistency observation only.","line":108}]},"followUpAttempts":0,"transientRetryAttempts":0},"startedAt":"2026-06-14T10:37:55.093Z","endedAt":"2026-06-14T10:44:32.569Z"}
